{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"过年顺口溜","authors":["阿毛"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":1,"day":9}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿毛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满街锣鼓咚咚呛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗万面齐飘扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭炮火花乒乓放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利新年真欢畅!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派，在上海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们工人过年如过关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平日里，吃不饱，穿不暖，典当借债度日受苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一到年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当要赎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"债要还，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当不赎，不要紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"债不还，就得坐牢监，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们工人，听说要过年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不愁眉苦脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不长吁短叹!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官僚，买办，洋流氓，老板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压榨我们还不算，最恨人:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不把我们当人看，抄身，检查，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们当做小偷看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有，洋流氓，奴才，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一高兴，举手就打咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他还说他是在练拳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们当成奴隶玩弄，摧残。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要不服气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一拍桌子，你就得滚蛋!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受尽侮辱，委曲求全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样一天又一天，一年又一年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到年间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"求他们给些“年赏”钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还得到他们府上去请愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼一瞪，口一张，就说:　 “ 工人反了天”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电话打到衙门去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警车，马队，木棍，皮鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们围在圈中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭抽，棍打还不算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要抓去代表坐牢监，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伤心事，一桩桩，一件件"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈指数不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈指数不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派，在上海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支票大钞满天飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物价也就涨上天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心搜刮，死人不管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿到可怜“年赏钱”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当也赎不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"债也还不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别说猪肉吃不起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斤牛年糕也难办。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终日劳苦一整年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到年来，家里厢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是缺柴，缺米，又缺盐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过年，过年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不愁眉哭脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不长吁短叹!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年过年，大家都喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派，落花流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个的都被打跑，滚蛋!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们工人把身翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当了主人翁，掌握了政权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俗话说的好:“饮水要思源”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是:响的党——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党救了咱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是:咱的军队——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军解放了咱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的恩情说不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的恩情说不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府是咱们自己的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切事情都要自己带头干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为反动派的破坏摧残，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我们留下重重困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要想突击建设，渡过难关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要厉行节约，增加生产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国大陆大部解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要继续解放西藏和台湾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这也需要我们来支援"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样克服困难?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样去支援?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除了增加生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要把公债来买。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买了折实公债，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等于自己存了款，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物价不涨，生活得到安全五年本利一齐还。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到那时吃不光，穿不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认购公债，与己有利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又可解决政府困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一举两得真好算盘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克服了困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就可繁荣经济，发展生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，来，来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工友们，我们带头干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到明年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过年，比今年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要快乐喜欢!"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}